    "\n",
    "## Key rules to carry forward {.smaller}\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Always move to device** — `model.to(device)` and `data.to(device)`\n",
    "2. **Normalize inputs** — ImageNet stats for pre-trained models, always\n",
    "3. **Augment training only** — validation data stays clean\n",
    "4. **Start with transfer learning** — only build from scratch when you must\n",
    "5. **`torch.no_grad()` for eval** — saves memory, prevents gradient tracking\n",
    "6. **Save state_dict, not the model** — `torch.save(model.state_dict(), path)`\n",
